Eyemart Express

How Do I Know If Eyemart Express Takes Insurance?

Whether Eyemart Express takes insurance depends on if they’re an optometrist or an ophthalmologist.

Optometrists perform your regular eye exams and write prescriptions for glasses. These doctors will accept vision insurance. An ophthalmologist, on the other hand, is a medical doctor; therefore, whether you’re covered depends on your standard medical insurance plan.

The best way to answer this question is to call Eyemart Express and ask them.

Does Eyemart Express have An Online Website?

To answer this question, try going to Google to search for Eyemart Express, or you can just call them and ask.

Does Eyemart Express Offer Extended Hours?

Sometimes you can look for extended hours for eye doctors on Google or at the website for Eyemart Express. But that information is often not updated correctly or quickly. The best thing to do is call them directly and ask.
